<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-05-1119 </DOCNO><TEXT>Using statistical data relevant to the national (Italian) consumptionof energy (from traditional sources) for industry, transportation systemsand housing, the authors point out inefficiencies and hazards. They thensuggest several proposals leading towards an improved energy policy whichwould incorporate the rational use and development of renewable energysources - geothermal, solar, wind, etc.</TEXT></DOC>